== Births == * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1838]] {{ill|April 13|ja|4月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Gotō Shōjirō|ja|後藤象二郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a politician and prominent figure in the Freedom and People's Rights Movement (died [[1897]]).
== Deaths == * [[Huangchu]] 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[223]] {{ill|May 6|ja|5月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Cao Ren|ja|曹仁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander from the Three Kingdoms period (born [[168]]). * [[Chiku]] 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[245]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Lu Xun|ja|陸遜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander and statesman (born [[183]]).
