== Births == * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 9th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1838]] [[:en:April 13|April 13]]) – [[:en:Gotō Shōjirō|Gotō Shōjirō]], a politician and prominent figure in the Freedom and People's Rights Movement (died [[1897]]).
== Deaths == * [[Huangchu]] 4th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[223]] [[:en:May 6|May 6]]) – [[:en:Cao Ren|Cao Ren]], a military commander from the Three Kingdoms period (born [[168]]). * [[Chiku]] 8th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[245]] [[:en:May 2|May 2]]) – [[:en:Lu Xun (Eastern Wu)|Lu Xun]], a military commander and statesman (born [[183]]).
